// KNOWN-GOOD Bedrock Configuration — Last verified: 2026-03-30
// Copy this block into preferences.jsonc env section to restore Bedrock.
// Profile: your-aws-profile | Account: REDACTED-AWS-ACCOUNT | Region: us-west-2
//
// To restore: replace the Bedrock section in preferences.jsonc with these values,
// then run: bun ~/.claude/hooks/handlers/BuildSettings.ts
